profile:
VIPremium Contracting has been providing concrete services to Central Vancouver Island for the past 40 years!  With hundreds of projects completed throughout the years, we take pride in the reputation we have built with businesses, subcontractors and homeowners!  We are committed to total customer satisfaction and are dedicated to maintaining commitments to our valued customers.
VIPremium Contracting is experienced and equipped to complete all residential and commercial projects with precision and detail! Our team is proficient in concrete repair, drainage, concrete finishing, curbs and sidewalks. From the bid estimation process to the complete construction, VIPremium Contracting is a team of knowledgeable and efficient specialists that are here to take you from start to finish for any yard makeover or concrete project.  We begin with a free evaluation and discuss best options to transpire your visions into a reality!
Our expertise in estimating, construction and project management ensures our customers receive quality work at a fair and competitive price. We take time to explain the process and provide you with cost effective options to ensure your project is completed to your satisfaction in a timely manner, within your budget.
Our work is built to last as proven and displayed in the many projects completed throughout Central Vancouver Island.  Check out our brickwork completed throughout downtown Nanaimo in 1982 – You’ll agree it’s still looking great almost 40 years later! We stand by our work and maintain the highest level of professionalism, integrity and fairness to our associates and clients.
